1967;;The Naked Runner;;British;;Sidney J. Furie;;Frank Sinatra, Edward Fox;;spy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Naked_Runner;;Sam Laker (Sinatra) is a former World War II Office of Strategic Services (OSS) operative who is recruited by his former commanding officer to do a mission whilst he attends a business conference in Leipzig. To ensure his cooperation, his son is kidnapped.